From 3ff42e1a71b6b27b8b64015fec2b4d5726c245b3 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: claude-bot <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Fri, 17 Apr 2026 23:41:38 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] phase-2: remove route-level mock data from risk_v2 and
 backtest_v2
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Phase 2 hardening for production readiness. The two highest-impact
"lying routes" — risk_v2 and backtest_v2 — were returning hardcoded
fixtures from inline JS objects. They now read from real engine
state and a runtime-populated results store.

New infrastructure:
- api-server/src/lib/demo_mode.ts
  hasLiveBroker(), demoDataAllowed(), markDemoResponse(),
  sendDemo(), require503IfNoBroker(). Single source of truth for
  the dev-vs-prod data decision.
- api-server/src/lib/risk_v2/state.ts
  Lazy-singleton risk engines. In production, clears the engine
  constructors' built-in mock portfolios so first sync starts
  clean. In dev, keeps demo positions visible.
- api-server/src/lib/backtest_v2/results_store.ts
  Per-process registry of backtest results, credibility/overfit/
  leakage/walk-forward/comparison reports. Empty in production
  until populated by EventDrivenBacktester runs. Seeds a single
  demo row in dev so the UI renders.

Route changes:
- api-server/src/routes/risk_v2.ts
  - Removed PORTFOLIO/POSITIONS/LIMITS/EVENTS/OVERNIGHT/TRADE_GATE
    inline fixtures (~115 lines of hardcoded JSON).
  - Now reads from getRiskV2State() — the real engine singletons.
  - Returns 503 in production if broker keys are missing.
  - Stamps every dev/test response with X-Demo-Data: true header
    and `_demo: true` body field.
- api-server/src/routes/backtest_v2.ts
  - Removed BACKTESTS/CREDIBILITY/OVERFIT/LEAKAGE/WALK_FORWARD/
    COMPARISON inline fixtures (~165 lines of hardcoded JSON).
  - Now reads from backtestResultsStore.
  - Production starts empty; dashboards see no fake "bt-001"
    success theatre.
  - Same X-Demo-Data + _demo stamping.

Production semantics:
- Production + valid broker keys  → real positions, real metrics.
- Production + missing keys       → 503 broker_not_configured.
- Development / test              → demo data, clearly stamped.

Verification:
- pnpm tsc --build → exit 0 (workspace clean)

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 <noreply@anthropic.com>
